			<h1 class="h-alpha">
		<a href="/docs/api/lithium/1.0.x/lithium" class="symbol-segment">lithium</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/1.0.x/lithium/template" class="symbol-segment">template</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/1.0.x/lithium/template/view" class="symbol-segment">view</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/1.0.x/lithium/template/view/Renderer" class="symbol-segment">Renderer</a>::applyHandler()		</h1>

